    "name": "归园田居",
    "steam_appid": 1879250,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏Q群：</h2>●1群：569106078<br>●2群：528363568<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >B站开发者：罗月先生</h2><br>开发者的话：<br>作为多年的经营和种田爱好者，一直梦想着有这么一个游戏：<br>身居陋屋，养鸡养鹅，采菊东篱下。<br>过了木桥便是古代小镇，有贩夫走卒，有江湖侠客，白日繁华兴盛，夜深渔舟唱晚，探索他们不同身份下所掩埋的故事。<br>穿过山道，道观中有一老道，唠唠叨叨，听说曾是绝世高手，荒郊破庙，有鬼怪寄居，各种奇闻异事，待一探究竟。<br>想太久了，不如开团做一个吧~！然后拉了一群志同道合的小伙伴，然后建立了一个狭迫但温暖的工作室，然后天天不同地域的人吵架这道菜应该是怎么做，然后《归园田居》就诞生了。<br><br>●游戏介绍：<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >归园田居，林间野趣</h2>清除杂树野草，开垦荒地，化作良田一片。<br>种植各具特色的农作物，灌溉施肥，静待硕果累累，还可修复水车，聆听溪水流淌于田野间的脆响，感受收获之喜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/3ba79ae26a5e200faa884415dffd169c.poster.avif?t=1758598741\" width=570 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/3ba79ae26a5e200faa884415dffd169c.webm?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/3ba79ae26a5e200faa884415dffd169c.mp4?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >烹饪美食，种茶制茶</h2>你可烹饪众多的地方美食，从小镇客栈、远道而来的胡商、甚至鬼市之中发现菜谱，解锁蒸笼、铁锅、烤炉等炊具。<br>在农场的左上方打造一个独立的茶园，在此种植茶叶，通过晒、酿、炒等方式加工制茶，泡一壶清茶，喊上三五挚友相聚，品茶赏月，乐得逍遥。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/9ec96d75b8de57280ece7660e5404368.poster.avif?t=1758598741\" width=570 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/9ec96d75b8de57280ece7660e5404368.webm?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/9ec96d75b8de57280ece7660e5404368.mp4?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >市井百态，策马同游</h2>古茶镇分为东西二市，西市鱼龙混杂，客栈赌坊、药铺佛寺，杂货小摊等一应俱全。东市繁华，可见青楼画舫、茶馆布庄、官府琼楼。<br>每个角色在镇子里拥有各自的喜好与行动轨迹，结为挚友，探索他们内心隐埋的故事。祥和闲适之下，或曾是江湖夜雨，铁马金戈。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/cec41a0a798c5f414846d2e4fef3a1e6.poster.avif?t=1758598741\" width=570 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/cec41a0a798c5f414846d2e4fef3a1e6.webm?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/cec41a0a798c5f414846d2e4fef3a1e6.mp4?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >养鸡养鹅，小猫小狗</h2>领养可爱的猫咪与小狗，建立深厚的感情后，它每日会为你带来各种稀奇古怪的物品，触发额外的奇闻趣事。<br>搭建家畜小屋，养殖动物，照料它们成长，可收获鸡蛋、羊奶、蚕丝等农产品，成为小镇上富甲一方的农场主人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/cdde3bcd9fc754603815fb03a381785d.poster.avif?t=1758598741\" width=570 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/cdde3bcd9fc754603815fb03a381785d.webm?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/cdde3bcd9fc754603815fb03a381785d.mp4?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >藏品收集，古董话本</h2>众多精美的古董，民俗话本等待你的收集~！它们常藏于你意料不到的地方。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/9eec03d0b26d9178a6e7a9578cb6cf79.poster.avif?t=1758598741\" width=570 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/9eec03d0b26d9178a6e7a9578cb6cf79.webm?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/9eec03d0b26d9178a6e7a9578cb6cf79.mp4?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >妖魔鬼怪，阴间诡事</h2>妖怪与人类以古茶镇的阴界为隔，阴界中的一切皆为小镇的倒影，每逢子时，阳气褪尽，阴间市集，凡人不可进入其中，但却售卖人间难寻的珍奇物品。<br>寻求与妖怪交流的办法，揭开阴阳市集的秘密，扭转曾与你有着莫大因果的宿命。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/b2f4029fe8f23bd3485fbaf8dfef2de5.poster.avif?t=1758598741\" width=570 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/b2f4029fe8f23bd3485fbaf8dfef2de5.webm?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879250/extras/b2f4029fe8f23bd3485fbaf8dfef2de5.mp4?t=1758598741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
